Detailed Description

Structure to specify the properties of the datastore. Corresponds to the DataStore element in the SyncML Device Information DTD.

Field Documentation

const SyncMLCTCap* _MSVC_CONST_FLAW SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_ct_cap
 

List of supported content type capabilities of this data store.

UINT32 SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_ct_cap_count
 

Number of SyncMLCTCap elements.

const CHAR* SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_display_name
 

Specifies the display name of the datastore. Corresponds to the DisplayName element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Optional!

UINT16 SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_max_guid_size
 

Specifies the maximum size of the global unique identifier for the datastore. Corresponds to the MaxGUIDSize element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Optional!

UINT32 SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_max_id
 

Specifies the maximum number of items that can be stored in the datastore. Corresponds to the MaxID element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Optional!

UINT32 SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_max_mem
 

Specifies the maximum memory size for a given local datastore, in bytes. Corresponds to the MaxMem element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Optional!

const SyncMLCTTypeVerCT* _MSVC_CONST_FLAW SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_rx
 

List of the supported types and versions of a content type which can be received by the device. Corresponds to the Rx element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Maybe empty!

UINT16 SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_rx_count
 

Number of SyncMLCTTypeVerCT elements.

const SyncMLCTTypeVerCT* _MSVC_CONST_FLAW SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_rx_pref
 

Specifies the preferred type and version of a content type received by the device. Corresponds to the Rx-Pref element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Mandatory!

BOOLEAN SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_shared_mem
 

Specifies if the datastore memory is shared with other data stores. Corresponds to the SharedMem element in the SyncML Device Information DTD.

const CHAR* SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_source_ref
 

Specifies the reference URI for the database. Corresponds to the SourceRef element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Mandatory!

BOOLEAN SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_support_large_objects
 

Specifies that the data store supports handling of large objects. Corresponds to the SupportLargeObjs element in the SyncML Device Information DTD.

const SyncMLSyncType* _MSVC_CONST_FLAW SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_sync_cap
 

Specifies the synchronization capabilities of the datastore in the form of a list of supported types of synchronization. Corresponds to the SyncCap element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Mandatory!

UINT16 SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_sync_type_count
 

Number of the SyncMLSyncType elements in m_sync_cap.

const SyncMLCTTypeVerCT* _MSVC_CONST_FLAW SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_tx
 

List of the supported types and versions of a content type which can be transmitted by the device. Corresponds to the Tx element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Maybe empty!

UINT16 SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_tx_count
 

Number of SyncMLCTTypeVerCT elements.

const SyncMLCTTypeVerCT* _MSVC_CONST_FLAW SyncMLDataStoreProps::m_tx_pref
 

Specifies the preferred type and version of a content type transmitted by the device. Corresponds to the Tx-Pref element in the SyncML Device Information DTD. Mandatory!
